      "text": "Spring Security  FilterChain  (stateless · CSRF off)\n• JwtAuthFilter  (extracts Bearer token, validates HS256)\n• AuthenticationManager  (BCrypt 10 rounds)\n• CorsFilter  (allowedOrigins = \"*\", expose Authorization)",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "baseline": 12,
      "containerId": "rect-4",
      "originalText": "Spring Security  FilterChain  (stateless · CSRF off)\n• JwtAuthFilter  (extracts Bearer token, validates HS256)\n• AuthenticationManager  (BCrypt 10 rounds)\n• CorsFilter  (allowedOrigins = \"*\", expose Authorization)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
