      "text": "DAO Layer  (Spring JdbcTemplate · 5 DAOs)\n• UserDao            (users)\n• SecurityDao        (v_security_score · v_cascade_risks)\n• PillarDao          (v_pillar1..v_pillar4 IEA/APERC views)\n• AlertDao           (alerts · v_active_alerts)\n• RecommendationDao  (recommendations · v_active_recommendations)",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "baseline": 12,
      "containerId": "rect-8",
      "originalText": "DAO Layer  (Spring JdbcTemplate · 5 DAOs)\n• UserDao            (users)\n• SecurityDao        (v_security_score · v_cascade_risks)\n• PillarDao          (v_pillar1..v_pillar4 IEA/APERC views)\n• AlertDao           (alerts · v_active_alerts)\n• RecommendationDao  (recommendations · v_active_recommendations)",
